  <div id="text-content_4E99EA50-1D70-0135-0D82-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Administrators can enable a warning reminding all users about preferred email addresses for notifications. When enabled, the next time users at that institution visit the Notification Settings page, they will see a popup alerting them that adding a non-institution based email address may result in the exposure of sensitive content.</p>
